snippet.title: Stones Keeper II: Chaos Lord - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In Stones Keeper II: Chaos Lord, you will find both the well-known game mechanics of the original game as well as many new features. A signature blend of RPG and strategy with turn-based tactical battles.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2779310/Stones_Keeper_II_Chaos_Lord/
